<ol id="fs-id2592707" type="a">
<li>a type AB mother is carrying a type O fetus</li>
<li>a type O mother is carrying a type AB fetus</li>
<li>an Rh<sup>+</sup> mother is carrying an Rh<sup>&#8722;</sup> fetus</li>
<li>an Rh<sup>&#8722;</sup> mother is carrying a second Rh<sup>+</sup> fetus</li>
